ComicInfo.Summary:
The Haunted Skyscraper: Jonah has his childhood home placed atop a skyscraper he owns and keeps his wife prisoner there.
Escape from the Grave: Pete Tupper fakes his death in an attempt to avoid execution.
Death Was in the Driver's Seat!: Harriet and Horace want to know what is the secret of the red box of Rosita's.
Face of Death: Arnold Bryant is tricked into plastic surgery to make him look like the dictator of a Latin American country.
Killer Pack: Colin Canis trains his dogs to attack the man who got him fired from his job.
Cruise of Corpses: Eric Halston plans his revenge against the three people he believe killed his wife with witchcraft.
The Killing Machine: Mr. Ezeel challenges four gamblers to a pinball contest.
A Deadly Game: Luke Haney pulls one to many practical jokes.
The Revenge of the Toymaker: The evil Emperor first kills Alberto's son, then Alberto himself, but Alberto's toys get their revenge.
Dead Man's Eyes!: Frank Bronson consults a fortune teller to advise him on the best time to move against a rival crime boss.
